  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec FR-11">DELETE `AnalysisOrchestrationService.ExecuteAnalysisAsync` — audit + migrate all callers to `PlaybookOrchestrationService.ExecuteAsync` via degenerate playbook OR consumer-routing dispatch.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-06">Backward compatibility NOT a concern. No transition shim; cleanly migrate or remove.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">BFF AI Architecture — `IInvokePlaybookAi` is the canonical AI invocation surface. All callers route through it (Invariant 1).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">BFF Publish Hygiene — verify publish-size delta at end of task (expected: NEGATIVE — removing direct-path call sites should slightly reduce binary size).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-038">Testing Strategy — caller test updates follow ADR-038 (mock IInvokePlaybookAi only; no Mock&lt;HttpMessageHandler&gt;; no DI-registration tests).</constraint>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §11">No new components introduced — modifying existing call sites to point at the canonical facade. Justification rule does not apply (modification, not new surface).</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md">Pre-merge checklist applies. Test update obligation per §F.6 — caller test updates MUST happen with code change, not deferred.</constraint>
  </constraints>

