  <context>
    <background>
      Task 040 produced the caller inventory. Wave 9 task 091 migrated the chat-summarize caller
      (the largest known caller). This task picks up any remaining non-chat callers identified by
      task 040 and migrates them using the same pattern Wave 9 established. If no other callers
      exist (entirely plausible — `ExecuteAnalysisAsync` may have been chat-only by R6), this task
      becomes a verification + no-op; document that and proceed.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="040" status="must-complete-first">Caller-audit document at notes/spikes/executeanalysisasync-caller-audit.md drives this task's scope.</dependency>
      <dependency task="091" status="must-complete-first">Wave 9 task 091 migrates SessionSummarizeOrchestrator (chat-summarize). DO NOT re-migrate it here. Per CLAUDE.md / TASK-INDEX.md, Wave 4 is intentionally ordered AFTER Wave 9.</dependency>
    </dependencies>
